name: Allure
description: When you have the attention you have attraction. Tempting beauty, vibe, emotion, nature, behavior, mistakes, and ugliness all get into the bucket when you accept someone. Allure is the artwork of temptation and seduction which have an expression of need with a colorful vibe of female nature. Vibrant colors on the face with eyes that speak the language of attraction. This artwork is made to attract people towards colors.
